title: Kim Iversen on Florida Grand Jury Investigating Criminal Actions of Pfizer and COVID-19 Vaccine Profiteers
cleaned_text: “Governor Ron DeSantis has announced he’s calling for a Grand Jury investigation that will look into Big Pharma’s possible wrongdoings regarding the COVID-19 vaccines, specifically misleading claims regarding efficacy and safety—all in the name of mandating the vaccines and making Big Pharma enormous amounts of money.”
